# Proxy agent → production

When you finish edits under `proxy-agent/`, run from repo root:

```bash
./scripts/deploy-proxy-agent-prod.sh
```

Prefer SSH key: run once `./scripts/setup-agent-prod-ssh.sh`. For passwordless sudo deploy, install `scripts/remote/nocko-agent-deploy-sync.sh` on the server — see `docs/agent-prod-ssh-and-sudo.md`.

Until then: `SSHPASS` + `PROD_AGENT_SUDO_PASS` (never commit).

Default target: `192.168.11.153` → `/opt/nocko-agent`, then `https://192.168.11.153:8443/` (TZ §6.2).
